<HEADLINE> Quick Facts on Cabela Catalog Co. </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	Some facts about Cabela's, a mail-order outdoor outfitting  
company: 
</P>
<P>
	--Headquarters in Sidney, Neb.  
</P>
<P>
	--Employs 3,265 people.  
</P>
<P>
	--Retail stores in Sidney; Kearney, Neb.; Owatonna, Minn.; and  
Prairie du Chien, Wis. A fifth store is planned in East Grand 
Forks, Minn. 
</P>
<P>
	--Telemarketing operations in Grand Island, Neb., and Kearney. A  
customer-service center in North Platte, Neb., and a merchandise 
returns facility in Oshkosh, Neb. 
</P>
<P>
	--Ships catalogs and goods to customers in all 50 states and 120  
countries. 
</P>
<P>
	-- Spokesmen include former University of Nebraska football coach  
Tom Osborne, and former Minnesota Vikings football coach Bud Grant. 
Both are hunters; Grant sometimes models clothing in Cabela's 
catalogs. 
</P>
</TEXT>
